{"tid":1651934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳幫手]有無人影到今日16:25荃灣有黑狗私家車借救護車開路直撞示威者既片?","createTime":"2019-10-13T13:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T13:40:30.000Z","uid":34816,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4cac3d7c7d8b438efc113df3ab4df35d0e185987","tid":1651934,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:34:05.000Z","msg":"上個po錯左時間，我重開sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左捉人，班死仆街黑狗到左今時今日既戰術已經毫無底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說今日16：25左右，手足係荃灣新之城對出青山公路荃灣段set左rb，然後突然聽到前面位置有救護車聲，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當車群讓路予救護車後，有數架私家狗車突然加速衝出直接衝開rb再不減速直接撞入示威人群到，速龍落車邊開槍邊拘捕</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於事出太突然真係無咩人影到相關片段，我跪求有影到既人士可唔可以拎出黎，一齊向傳媒國際線等煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足你地以後set rb要set得厚d同實淨d，唔係班狗真係無性架，會直接撞過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋如非必要真係唔好再讓任何車輛通過。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你班死黑狗你地死全家都唔撚夠還，有影到車牌既手足幫手上報果幾架仆街狗車，唔好以為唔撚洗還</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c39bbd11584dadc1f9f6f45da5a55b26e2751b0b","tid":1651934,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:34:39.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d6711547e584f026671d4042ab5bc4a0a2118251","tid":1651934,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:34:49.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"4338a5ae53ad40748dad855ee022482add3804f0","tid":1651934,"uid":105905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse